Rating: 4
Great taste for such an easy, quick recipe. Not sure why other reviewers described this as bland. I will say, however, that it tasted better on the second day. I chose to buy pre-cooked shrimp and let them marinate in the garlic, oil, oregano mix then added them right before serving. I also spent an extra 10 minutes reducing the sauce because otherwise it is a bit too watery. Overall, a tasty recipe I will certainly make again.

